{"tid":1561664,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我係救護，關於831，我有嘢講","createTime":"2019-09-11T16:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T18:01:48.000Z","uid":267047,"like":21,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7ac91d8fdcde8c48a8a489fa8dabdfd591a05d","tid":1561664,"uid":267047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"消防救護朋友冇Ac 所以代post，大家自行判斷。<br />\n<br />\n過去各大大小小MCI(multiple casualty incident) 都會出現報數同埋數時有出入，原因可以好多。我地內部有一句說話，混亂中完成，都適用於各大小場面。<br />\n<br />\n講返831，救護到場後被警察阻止入站，要一個PAO見習救護主任（主任級既最低層）爭取到佢自己一個人落去站入面走一轉作初步點算人數及傷勢，大家知唔知有幾難？壓力會有幾大？一個人要行晒兩層4個月台要幾耐？真係唔會出錯？人數真係會唔變？佢見到既傷者係被捕左？可以自由走動？站入面其實真係仲係好亂，唔會10個傷者坐定定係度俾你數。大家反而要讚佢堅持講數講贏個警察放佢落去，如果唔係唔知仲要等幾耐先有得落去。<br />\n<br />\n今日毛議員俾大家睇左張檢傷分類卡，有講到個檢傷標準係點，但有時我地去幫病人分流，都會over triage, 所以紅色傷者又係唔係真係唔可以走動？傷者傷勢可以升級或降級，甚至到最後唔去醫院都有，所以，咁樣傷者數目有出入一d都唔奇。<br />\n<br />\n我反而著眼另一個位，就係要送傷者去荔枝角上救護車送院。點解里d決策要由一個一粒仔去傾去咩飛？其他高級d既SAO， Supt. 去左邊？大家覺得一個一粒仔夠牙力係現場同警察傾？冇錯，現場秩序從來都係警察負責，但當傷者到左我地手，我地都有一定既話事權吧。d 救護官去左邊？<br />\n<br />\n最後，救護入埸前發生咩事，只得警察同港鐵先知。如果有人死又要滅救護聲既，一定冇可能，因為我地部門入面唔似警察一言堂，我地可以大聲表達自己，更何況有死人仲要幫手隱瞞，我相信我地d兄弟一定會出聲！總之，到場兄弟肯定見唔到有死人，但被人清左或收埋呢就另計，千其唔好俾人拖埋落水。<br />\n<br />\n唔好射錯目標，咁樣會令事情帶來反後果，失去更多市民支持。消防處從來對外答問題都好屎，因為佢來來去去都係得幾個答案，現場環境危險，極度高溫，遠離水源，灌救有難度等等等等，要會佢地答d政治野隨時炒車....<br />\n<br />\n要數人數，不如數下幾多人入左新屋嶺出唔返黎好過.....個條數可能仲鬼。<br />\n<br />\n結論：到場兄弟肯定見唔到有死人，清左或收埋就另計。"},{"pid":"714bfabde516d0e277243d10a90ab66f15813e1d","tid":1561664,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:27:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qftu6C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqftu6C0.jpg&h=23ce3992&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvOSjYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcvOSjYn.jpg&h=c1edffca&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FeMP6D2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFeMP6D2.jpg&h=0810fe9c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmPmXLP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmPmXLP.png&h=5f6e170e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYO68T8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYO68T8.jpg&h=b22b9f08&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZn4be8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZn4be8.jpg&h=a1744d81&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9nr81V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9nr81V.jpg&h=7475a820&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p55dO38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp55dO38.jpg&h=e72515fd&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9dc01685779ed15f6d22fe66cddc977b33426270","tid":1561664,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited